extendedInfo.description: Why waste money, time and energy when you can make life simple by using Career Cat.Over 40% of students who graduate from college do not pursue jobs relating to their majors. Career Cat will simplify your career search by guiding you through a path of selected interests of your choice to reach your desired occupations. At the end of your journey, it will produce occupations and salaries that are suitable to your interests.Have a career question that you want us to answer? Check out our message board to find answers, tips and information on any career that you are interested in! Our app will forward you to our website directly if you choose. The website is c-b123.com.Start your career search with Career Cat!

reviews.title: Excellent app.
reviews.comment: There is so much information on this app about careers. It is organized well and I have been waiting for a good reference like this for a while.
reviews.author: Alex Jeffrey

reviews.title: Great for my kids!
reviews.comment: This app has allowed my kids to explore options in terms of education and career choices.  Wish I had an app like this when I was in school. Great app!
reviews.author: Liv Loxx

reviews.comment: Wow i let my 3 kids try this app and it really did  help them  with guidance and gave some good different jobs i didnt even know about. Pass the word about this app cause it could help alot of peoples lives. I wish i came up with the idea....
reviews.author: A Google User
